OL,3,CCare worker jailed after being filmed
OL,4,Cabusing elderly patient
OL,6,FA care worker has been sent to prison
OL,7,Fafter he was caught on film physically
OL,8,Fabusing an elderly patient.
OL,10,FJinu Shaji, aged 26, of Russet Avenue,
OL,11,FExeter, was convicted of ill-treatment
OL,12,Fat Exeter Magistrates' Court and has
OL,13,Fnow been sentenced at Exeter Crown
OL,14,FCourt.
OL,16,FThe victim, 94, was partially-sighted
OL,17,Fand had limited physical mobility. He
OL,18,Fwas a resident at Langford Park
OL,19,Fnursing home in Devon.
