OL,3,CCare worker jailed after being filmed
OL,4,Cabusing elderly patient
OL,6,FIn July 2023, his family installed a
OL,7,Fcamera and recorded the abuse after
OL,8,Fnoticing bruising on the victim's leg.
OL,10,FThe footage showed the man being
OL,11,Fhandled roughly and being treated with
OL,12,Fa lack of dignity and respect.
OL,14,FThe family immediately reported this
OL,15,Fto the care home manager and Shaji was
OL,16,Fsuspended.
OL,18,FThree other care workers, who were
OL,19,Femployed by an agency, were reported,
OL,20,Fand told not to return to the home
OL,21,Fwith immediate effect.
