OL,6,FShaji was later charged with ill-
OL,7,Ftreatment by a care worker and
OL,8,Fappeared at Exeter Magistrates' Court
OL,9,Fon 21 December 2023. The other three
OL,10,Freceived police cautions for ill-
OL,11,Ftreatment/neglect by a care worker.
OL,13,FDetective Inspector Charlotte Heath
OL,14,Fsaid: "This was an extremely upsetting
OL,15,Fcase which showed distressing footage
OL,16,Fof the victim being roughly handled by
OL,17,Fthose who should have been caring for
OL,18,Fhim.
